commentTextItems.html: sees a bit of air on the ball and opens the face, driving in the air between cover and point and that's the end of the game

commentPostTextItems.html: Hussey pumps his fist as he runs across. Another not out for him. Australia go up 1-0 with a clinical run chase. Superb effort from White. Should be the Man of the Match, I'd say. Afridi's big hitting late in the Pakistan innings helped the tourists set Australia a target of 275 but they won with five wickets and nine deliveries in hand. White paced his innings beautifully, all Hussey had to do was knock the ball around and not lose his wicket. The fans lap up this win. Australia keep rolling.
That's all we have for you. Do join us for the second game which is on Sunday. Thanks for your company and we look forward to bringing you the coverage for the Sydney game. Bye for now!
